<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verification Code</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #007bff;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Your Verification Code</h1>
      <p>Please use the code below to reset your password. This code will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>
      <div class="code"><%= OTPDigits %></div>
      <p>If you did not request this code, please ignore this email or contact our support team for assistance.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />Your Company Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
